centos install 時　ネットワーク設定

yum update
yum upgrade
yum install net-tools


teraterm install
ssh root login OK
vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config
PermitRootLogin yes
PermitEmptyPasswords no
PasswordAuthentication yes
